snippet: Clemson fans are used to the sight: defensive coordinator Brent Venables charging onto the field in an emotional outburst, being pulled back to the sideline by the assistant strength coach in charge of keeping the intense coach out of trouble....
lead_paragraph: Clemson fans are used to the sight: defensive coordinator Brent Venables charging onto the field in an emotional outburst, being pulled back to the sideline by the assistant strength coach in charge of keeping the intense coach out of trouble.

headline.main: Clemson's D-Coordinator Brings Intensity and Then Some
